description: Enables your end user to provide feedback on their Amazon Q Business generated chat responses.

parameters.name: applicationId
parameters.description: The identifier of the application associated with the feedback.

parameters.name: conversationId
parameters.description: The identifier of the conversation the feedback is attached to.

parameters.name: messageId
parameters.description: The identifier of the chat message that the feedback was given for.

parameters.name: messageUsefulness
parameters.description: The feedback usefulness value given by the user to the chat message. The usefulness value assigned by an end user to a message. reason (string) --- The reason for a usefulness rating. comment (string) --- A comment given by an end user on the usefulness of an AI-generated chat message. The timestamp for when the feedback was submitted.

nested_params.name: usefulness
nested_params.description: The usefulness value assigned by an end user to a message.

nested_params.name: reason
nested_params.description: The reason for a usefulness rating.

nested_params.name: comment
nested_params.description: A comment given by an end user on the usefulness of an AI-generated chat message.

nested_params.name: submittedAt
nested_params.description: The timestamp for when the feedback was submitted.
